+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01UTCMzQQWsLXju5pJ849n2i","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's my architecture design:\n\n**File structure:**\n- `src/db.ts` - Database initialization + queries (using better-sqlite3)\n- `src/ot.ts` - Operational Transform engine (insert/delete operations, transform function)\n- `src/routes.ts` - Express REST routes for document CRUD + version history\n- `src/ws.ts` - WebSocket handler for real-time collaboration\n- `src/server.ts` - `createApp` factory function, ties everything together\n- `src/__tests__/server.test.ts` - Comprehensive tests\n\n**OT Design:**\n- Operations: `{type: 'insert', position: number, text: string}` and `{type: 'delete', position: number, count: number}`\n- Each document tracks a server version number\n- Clients send ops with their base version; server transforms against any concurrent ops\n- Broadcast transformed ops to all other connected clients\n\n**WebSocket Protocol:**\n- Connect to `/ws/:docId`\n- Server sends `{type: 'sync', content, version}` on connect\n- Client sends `{type: 'operation', operation, version}`\n- Server broadcasts `{type: 'operation', operation, version, clientId}` to others\n- Server sends `{type: 'ack', version}` to sender\n- Server sends `{type: 'error', message}` on invalid ops\n\nLet me now delegate implementation to Gemini, file by file."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":385,"cache_read_input_tokens":21563,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":385},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86e173e1-38a5-4c3c-9b95-74f5ae49777b","uuid":"16c5a219-e87a-4d3a-9851-34be18acbd47"}
